					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Given that the BU3270 inside the NES2/Famicom AV connects to CPU D2, you've got a substantially more annoying project here.<br />You'll either need to completely remove the BU3270, or completely replace how it handles D2.<br /><br />I'm not certain what the differences are between the BU3266 and the BU3270, if any.<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://vaot.mydns.jp/fc/nfau.htm">http://vaot.mydns.jp/fc/nfau.htm</a><!-- m --> has some terrifying(ly awesome?) rework.</div>

